abstract_ssm: This collection consists of 84 black and white photographs of New York scenes between 1950-1996.  The photographs were taken in Manhattan, Queens and Brooklyn and depict people in cafeterias and automats, subway scenes, biking, kids playing in a hydrant, and various protests.
